<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.7.1">
<l>tiruvuk kumtiru vākiya celvā teyvat tukkara cēceyya kaṇṇā</l>
<l>uruvac ceñcuṭa rāḻival lāṉē yulakuṇ ṭavoru vātiru mārpā</l>
<l>voruvaṟ kāṟṟiyuy yumvakai yeṉṟā luṭaṉiṉ ṟaivareṉ ṉuḷpukun toḻiyā</l>
<l>taruvit tiṉṟiṭa vañciniṉ ṉaṭaintē ṉaḻuntūr mēlticai niṉṟavam māṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Treasure who is fortune for [the lady of] fortune, king of gods,</l>
<l rend="indent">[you of] bright eyes,</l>
<l>Master of the shapely, red-flamed discus, singular [lord] who ate the world,</l>
<l rend="indent">[you with] Tiru at your chest,</l>
<l>If there is a way of [some]one escaping [and] being saved,</l>
<l rend="indent">I have resorted to you,</l>
<l>Fearing that  the five [senses], always surging in me without end,</l>
<l rend="indent">vexing [me], together will grind [me] down,</l>
<l rend="indent">lord who stands at the west side of Aḻuntūr.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
